OL,3,C'Pressure release valve': The new law
OL,4,Cguaranteeing leave for unpaid carers
OL,6,FITV News' Catherine Walker spoke to
OL,7,Fcarers about what the change in the
OL,8,Flaw means for them.
OL,10,FA new law giving up to two million
OL,11,Femployees with unpaid caring
OL,12,Fresponsibilities 'carers leave' has
OL,13,Fbeen hailed a "pressure release valve"
OL,14,Ffrom the "constant juggle".
OL,16,FThe Carers Leave Act, which starts on
OL,17,F6 April, will enable unpaid carers to
OL,18,Fask for up to five days leave from
OL,19,Ftheir employer - with it also
OL,20,Fprotecting them from dismissal for
OL,21,Ftaking the leave.
