OL,3,C'Pressure release valve': The new law
OL,4,Cguaranteeing leave for unpaid carers
OL,6,FCarer Laura Barnes, from , says it
OL,7,Fwill relieve some of the unrelenting
OL,8,Fpressure.
OL,10,FShe has had to strike a delicate
OL,11,Fbalance between her full time job and
OL,12,Fher role as an unpaid carer for her
OL,13,FGrandmother Joan.
OL,15,F"It's a constant juggle," she said.
OL,16,F"In fact I have basically two more-
OL,17,Fthan full time jobs - that's how I
OL,18,Fsort of describe it.
