OL,3,C'Pressure release valve': The new law
OL,4,Cguaranteeing leave for unpaid carers
OL,6,FAn estimated two million employees are
OL,7,Fin a similar position to Laura, and it
OL,8,Fis hoped this new law will allow them
OL,9,Fto stay in work while also acting as a
OL,10,Fcarer.
OL,12,FCarers UK led the campaign that saw
OL,13,FCarer's Leave be made a legal right,
OL,14,Fand consulted on the act as it made
OL,15,Fits way through parliament.
OL,17,FThe director of policy at Carers UK,
OL,18,FEmily Holzhausen OBE, said: "For the
OL,19,Ffirst time employers will have to
OL,20,Fthink about unpaid carers in their
OL,21,Fwork force.
