OL,3,C'Pressure release valve': The new law
OL,4,Cguaranteeing leave for unpaid carers
OL,6,F"This is incredibly important because
OL,7,F600 people a day give up work because
OL,8,Fthey're unable to juggle work and
OL,9,Fcare, so it's going to help people to
OL,10,Fmanage their caring lives as well as
OL,11,Fstay in work."
OL,13,FHowever, Employment Services Director
OL,14,FKate Palmer has warned a lack of
OL,15,Fknowledge around the new law could
OL,16,Fcause issues for some employers.
OL,18,FShe said: "I can honestly say I've
OL,19,Fspoken to many SME's (small and
OL,20,Fmidsize enterprises) of late who have
OL,21,Fno idea this is coming in.
