OL,3,C'Pressure release valve': The new law
OL,4,Cguaranteeing leave for unpaid carers
OL,6,F"More awareness is needed, because
OL,7,Fcarers have this right and its
OL,8,Fimportant they know about it.
OL,10,F"But also if employers don't know
OL,11,Fabout it they could absolutely be
OL,12,Ftaken off guard by it and it may
OL,13,Fcreate risk for their businesses."
OL,15,FThe new law will give carers official
OL,16,Frights at work, while it is unpaid and
OL,17,Fmay not help everybody, carers like
OL,18,FLaura say they hope it will spark a
OL,19,Fwider conversation about how those who
OL,20,Ftake care of others are looked after
OL,21,Fthemselves.
